    <body>
        <h1>{$node_name}</h1>
	<p>The module "Email Stats" shows statistic graphics of the quantity of incoming emails.</p>
	<p>The first graphic shows the amount of incoming emails of the last 26 hours and it is updated every hour. You will see this graphic from 3 hours later of installing this module.</p>
	<p>The second graphic shows the amount of incoming emails of the last 7 days and it is updated every 6 hours. You will see this graphic from 13 hours later of installing this module.</p>
	<p>The third graphic shows the amount of incoming emails of the last 12 months and it is updated every 15 days. You will see this graphic from 1 month later of installing this module.</p>
	<p>The message "Nothing to show yet" means that Elastix doesn't have the enough information to show these statistics.</p>
	<div class="hlp_figures"><img src="../modules/{$node_id}/images/hlp_email_stats.png" border="0" />
